text:
College Point Causeway (South 13th Street), at the S.E. corner of 25th Road (Ninth Ave.) This is a set of three views at angles that clearly show the complete exterior. In 1789 it was erected by Epilaphet Stratton; in 1873 it was the residence of E. Platt Stratton. It was demolished in 1924.

1922.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
title: Queens: College Point Causew - 25th Road
